      <figure class="post-media"> 
       <a href="http://ucsciencetoday.com/post/111873138302/a-view-that-can-boost-the-bodys-immune-response"><img src="http://41.media.tumblr.com/edddfcf89b07d07a008bb179bf1c93ff/tumblr_nk8k06dquH1tyfnalo1_500.jpg" alt="A view that can boost the body&amp;#8217;s immune response? ucberkeley researchers have found that the awe we feel when we&amp;#8217;re in nature (or viewing art or listening to music) may 
