     <article class="post text" id="110911873552"> 
      <div class="post-content"> 
       <h2><a href="http://ucsciencetoday.com/post/110911873552/whew">Whew!</a></h2> 
       <p>Today, we’re recording program number 1400. To give you some perspective, it took two years from program 1300 to 1400. Five segments per week, two years….you do the math. Thanks for tuning in. Now…champagne, anyone?<br></p> 
      </div> 
      <footer class="post-foot"> 
       <ul class="post-meta"> 
        <li><a href="http://ucsciencetoday.com/post/110911873552/whew" title="Friday, 13 February 2015 @ 13:15:00">13 Feb 2015 / 2 notes</a></li> 
        <li class="post-like-btn"><a href="https://www.tumblr.com/reblog/110911873552/rB3oKaq9" class="reblog_button" style="display: block;width:16px;height:16px;">
